== Trivia == * Majestia and Knightowl are the only superheroes mentioned in the [[Miraculous: Tales of Ladybug & Cat Noir|series]], but neither them or any other non-Miraculous superheroes have appeared in the series yet, only appearing in the comic books. * As mentioned by Victory in the third issue of ''[[Miraculous Adventures]]'', there are a lot of superheroes from around the world, many of them coming to help defeat the [[Kenya's father|Trash Krakken]].
